app_name: Groups Control Groups Voice Recording and Karaoke Apps Karaoke One
app_description: Sing the greatest hits of artists like Ariana Grande Harry Styles The Weeknd and many others! WHY CHOOSE KARAOKE ONE Do you feel like you could be the next Lady Gaga Karaoke One gives you the chance to show off your talent have fun with your friends climb the weekly charts and win amazing prizes by challenging artists from all over the world! All you need is your smartphone and your voice! HOW DOES KARAOKE ONE WORK Karaoke One is an absolute must have for anyone who loves to sing! Free song updates every month make this application the best you can find on this app store! Karaoke One is quick and easy: 1. Sign up on the app it s very easy all you need is a few clicks 2. Choose from our catalog the song you want to sing 3. Have fun recording your performance 4. Publish your video and show your talent! TEST YOUR TALENT WITH THE GREATEST HITS: choose your favorite song between pop hip hop trap rock rap country and more in order to voice your talent! Search into our catalog or choose from our playlists at your disposal and challenge your friends! Top 10 Hits in our catalog: Watermelon Sugar Harry Styles Stupid Love Lady Gaga Running Up That Hill Kate Bush Happy Pharrell Williams Creep Radiohead Drivers License Olivia Rodrigo Cake By The Ocean DNCE Good as Hell Lizzo Shake it Off Taylor Swift Dance Monkey Tones and I Best Karaoke Songs Ever: Total Eclipse of the Heart Bonnie Tyler My Way Frank Sinatra Baby One More Time Britney Spears I Will Survive Gloria Gaynor Losing My Religion R.E.M. Single Ladies Beyonce Bohemian Rhapsody Queen It s a Raining Men The Weather Girls CLIMB THE GLOBAL RANKINGS: with Karaoke One you ll be able to become a true international star and climb the weekly and monthly charts by showing off your musical talent and challenging artists from all over the world! RECORD AND PUBLISH YOUR PERFORMANCE: record and publish your video and in a few seconds you ll prove your talent to everyone! Download Karaoke One and become the star you ve always dreamed to be!
